object.name: FAQ.How do I create a Group

property.answer:
{{warning}}In order to create a group you must be logged in with an Administrator account.{{/warning}}
On the home page click on //Manage Groups//
[[image:manage groups.png]]
You will be taken to this page where you can enter the name for your new group and press //Create//
[[image:create.png]]
You will then be taken to a page where you can enter details about the group and add members to the group.
